<root>
   <descrip><person>Hildebrand,</person> Who was frightened by a <vehicle>Passing Motor,</vehicle> and was brought to Reason. </descrip>
   <lg num="1">
      <l num="1">“Oh, Murder! What was that, <person>Papa!</person>”</l>
      <l num="2"> “My child, It was a <vehicle>Motor-Car,</vehicle></l>
      <l num="3">A Most Ingenious Toy!</l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-40.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a <vehicle>car</vehicle> speeding down the road</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="2">
      <l num="1">Designed to Captivate and Charm </l>
      <l num="2"> Much rather than to rouse Alarm</l>
      <l num="3"> In any <person>English Boy.</person></l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-41.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a <person>man</person> with his hand on a <person>childs</person> head</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="3">
      <l num="1">“What would your <person>Great Grandfather</person> who </l>
      <l num="2">Was Aide-de-Camp to <person>General Brue,</person></l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-42.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a <career>general</career> on a <animal>horse</animal></interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="4">
      <l num="1">And lost a leg at <place>Waterloo,</place> </l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-43.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a <person>man</person> hopping on one leg</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="5">
      <l num="1">And <place>Quatre-Bras</place> and</l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-44.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a <person>man</person> hopping on one leg again</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="6">
      <l num="1"><place>Ligny</place> too!</l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-45.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a <person>man</person> hopping on one leg and falling</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="7">
      <l num="1">And died at <place>Trafalgar!</place>—</l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-46.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a <person>man</person> being shot on a bridge</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="8">
      <l num="1"> What would he have remarked to hear</l>
      <l num="2">His Young Descendant shriek with fear,</l>
      <l num="3">Because he happened to be near</l>
      <l num="4">A Harmless <vehicle>Motor-Car!</vehicle></l>
      <l num="5">But do not fret about it! Come!</l>
      <l num="6">We’ll off to Town And purchase some!”</l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-47.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a <person>man</person> and a <person>young boy</person> with a line of cars behind them</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
